column2: SELECT   p.objid, p.ra, p.dec,  p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.err_u,p.err_g,p.err_r,p.err_i,p.err_z,  p.petroFlux_u,p.petroFlux_g,p.petroFlux_r,p.petroFlux_i,p.petroFlux_z,  p.petroRad_u,petroRad_g,petroRad_r,petroRad_i,petroRad_z,  p.petroRadErr_u,p.petroRadErr_g,p.petroRadErr_r,p.petroRadErr_i,p.petroRadErr_z,  p.deVRad_u,p.deVRad_g,p.deVRad_r,p.deVRad_i,p.deVRad_z,  p.deVRadErr_u,p.deVRadErr_g,p.deVRadErr_r,p.deVRadErr_i,p.deVRadErr_z,  p.expRad_u,p.expRad_g,p.expRad_r,p.expRad_i,p.expRad_z,  p.expRadErr_u,p.expRadErr_g,p.expRadErr_r,p.expRadErr_i,p.expRadErr_z,  p.fracDeV_u,p.fracDeV_g,p.fracDeV_r,p.fracDeV_i,p.fracDeV_z,  s.specobjid, s.class,s.z as z_spec,s.zErr as zspec_err,  ga.bptclass, ga.oh_p5#, ga.lgm_tot_p5#, ga.lgm_fib_p5#,  ga.sfr_tot_p5#, sfr_fib_p5#, specsfr_tot_p5# FROM PhotoObjAll AS p  JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS ga ON ga.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE  s.z BETWEEN # AND #   AND s.class = &&&  AND p.dec < #  AND ga.lgm_tot_p5# BETWEEN # AND #  AND oh_p5# > #
